Download the friends and followers in a period of time by category

get_friends_followers_all.Rd

This download a time series with the evolution of friends, followers, listed, statuses, likes and the created date of the account with the possibility of download the historic data by category

get_friends_followers_all(category = "all", country = "ar", historic = F)

Arguments

category

A character with the category selected -"deputies","senators","national executive","others","province servants", "all"-
country

A character with the Alpha 2 code of the country that wants to download
historic

A logical value. Would you prefer the historic data?

Value

This function returns a data.frame including columns:

  • date

  • followers_count

  • friends_count

  • listed_count

  • statuses_count

  • favourites_count

  • account_created_at

See also

get_friends_followers

Examples

get_friends_followers_all(category = 'others',  historic = TRUE)
